query:
INSERT INTO transportation (tripId, type, name, fromLocation, toLocation, departureDate, departureTime, arrivalDate, arrivalTime, confirmationNumber, price, currency, notes, createdAt, updatedAt)
SELECT tripId, 'car' as type, company as name, pickupLocation as fromLocation, dropoffLocation as toLocation, pickupDate as departureDate, pickupTime as departureTime, dropoffDate as arrivalDate, dropoffTime as arrivalTime, confirmationNumber, price, currency, notes, createdAt, updatedAt
FROM car_rentals
WHERE tripId = 30001;
